1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:08,050
Chapter 3 Build Confidence and Destroy Fear Friends mean well when they say,

2
00:00:08,320 --> 00:00:13,011
it's only your imagination, don't worry, there's nothing to be afraid of.

3
00:00:13,601 --> 00:00:18,290
But you and I know this kind of fear medicine never really works.

4
00:00:18,641 --> 00:00:24,771
Such soothing remarks may give us fear relief for a few minutes or maybe even a few hours,

5
00:00:25,121 --> 00:00:32,051
but the it's only in your imagination treatment doesn't really build confidence and cure fear.

6
00:00:32,561 --> 00:00:38,530
Yes, fear is real and we must recognize it exists before we can conquer it.

7
00:00:39,201 --> 00:00:41,971
Most fear today is psychological.

8
00:00:42,241 --> 00:00:49,091
Worry, tension, embarrassment, panic, all stem from mismanaged negative imagination.

9
00:00:49,361 --> 00:00:53,731
But simply knowing the breeding ground of fear doesn't cure fear.

10
00:00:54,001 --> 00:01:00,130
If a physician discovers you have an infection in some part of your body, he doesn't stop there.

11
00:01:00,241 --> 00:01:03,570
He proceeds with treatment to cure the infection.

12
00:01:04,240 --> 00:01:10,691
The old it's only in your mind treatment presumes fear doesn't really exist, but it does.

13
00:01:10,960 --> 00:01:12,451
Fear is real.

14
00:01:12,721 --> 00:01:15,731
Fear is success enemy number one.

15
00:01:16,001 --> 00:01:19,570
Fear stops people from capitalizing on opportunity.

16
00:01:19,761 --> 00:01:22,371
Fear wears down physical vitality.

17
00:01:22,561 --> 00:01:28,130
Fear actually makes people sick, causes organic difficulties, shortens life.

18
00:01:28,401 --> 00:01:31,811
Fear closes your mouth when you want to speak.

19
00:01:32,561 --> 00:01:39,171
Fear, uncertainty, lack of confidence, explains why we still have economic recessions.

20
00:01:39,521 --> 00:01:44,771
Fear explains why millions of people accomplish little and enjoy little.

21
00:01:45,281 --> 00:01:48,371
Truly, fear is a powerful force.

22
00:01:48,561 --> 00:01:53,971
In one way or another, fear prevents people from getting what they want from life.

23
00:01:54,641 --> 00:01:59,490
Fear of all kinds and sizes is a form of psychological infection.

24
00:01:59,761 --> 00:02:07,090
We can cure a mental infection the same way we cure a body infection, with specific proved treatments.

25
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:13,731
First, though, as part of your pre-treatment preparation, condition yourself with this fact.

26
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:17,011
All confidence is acquired, developed.

27
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:19,650
No one is born with confidence.

28
00:02:19,921 --> 00:02:27,331
Those people you know who radiate confidence, who have conquered worry, who are at ease everywhere and all the time,

29
00:02:27,521 --> 00:02:30,370
acquired their confidence, every bit of it.

30
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:32,210
You can too.

31
00:02:32,480 --> 00:02:34,451
This chapter shows how.

